snippet.title: Bananas de Pijamas (SNES Bootleg)
snippet.description:
Another bootleg game? Why, yes.
This time, we're looking at a SNES Bootleg by the name of Bananas de Pijamas, which apparently is a kids television show about twin bananas... In pajamas.

This game is a ROM hack of "Chester Cheetah - Too Cool to Fool". From what I can tell, it's the same exact game, just with different graphics for the main collectables, character, HUD and it starts on a different stage, but I may be wrong.

If you want to play this game, you can play it here: http://www.vizzed.com/playonlinegames/game.php?id=64029&ref=282619
